Name: Food Ration Bar
Desc: Reduces Cooldown for Grapple by 25% for a designated Resonator for 30m. Only effective on your own Resonators in Co-Op Mode.
Bg: A staple food of the Jinzhou Garrison. Besides a hearty bite, it is also easy to make and carry around. Each serving comes with a message about guarding the homeland and a reminder to the soldiers that although the night is long and endless, Jinzhou always has their back.
